{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:51:10.718517+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:PqvMqK | {\"sha\":\"c967e1e67d179b75ccef9664f2cd4cac039bc74c\",\"truncated\":false,\"tree\":[{\"path\":\".github\",\"type\":\"tree\",\"mode\":\"040000\",\"sha\":\"91a71f271949fbd3a42c4ede8667cf661b3f43e1\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/trees/91a71f271949fbd3a42c4ede8667cf661b3f43e1\"},{\"path\":\".gitignore\",\"type\":\"blob\",\"size\":58,\"mode\":\"100644\",\"sha\":\"0692b6ee71425493946409022b36518e757464f9\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/blobs/0692b6ee71425493946409022b36518e757464f9\"},{\"path\":\"LICENSE\",\"type\":\"blob\",\"size\":694,\"mode\":\"100644\",\"sha\":\"b6d9fc662720f011377219850e6440e8bcd29985\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/blobs/b6d9fc662720f011377219850e6440e8bcd29985\"},{\"path\":\"README.md\",\"type\":\"blob\",\"size\":1647,\"mode\":\"100644\",\"sha\":\"dd8f230ebcee1ed2c87953be052ec8d2681c21fc\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/blobs/dd8f230ebcee1ed2c87953be052ec8d2681c21fc\"},{\"path\":\"profiles.toml\",\"type\":\"blob\",\"size\":622,\"mode\":\"100644\",\"sha\":\"761394d4c1bc093dffd57dd9d470512c6d645aaf\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/blobs/761394d4c1bc093dffd57dd9d470512c6d645aaf\"},{\"path\":\"pyproject.toml\",\"type\":\"blob\",\"size\":367,\"mode\":\"100644\",\"sha\":\"0b500f394f922700d7a473d309c410516f2f253c\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/blobs/0b500f394f922700d7a473d309c410516f2f253c\"},{\"path\":\"src\",\"type\":\"tree\",\"mode\":\"040000\",\"sha\":\"536b3ef4204df666c3df97fe84336f2584b41bcf\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/trees/536b3ef4204df666c3df97fe84336f2584b41bcf\"},{\"path\":\"tests\",\"type\":\"tree\",\"mode\":\"040000\",\"sha\":\"824affde746d1b830a6d8531726a66827ff2017a\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/git/trees/824affde746d1b830a6d8531726a66827ff2017a\"}],\"tree_sha\":\"main\",\"owner\":\"rpnr-bench\",\"repo\":\"T10_R01_C03_A03\",\"recursive\":false,\"count\":8}", "id": "lc_6f859d4c-2b27-4402-90ce-70820a88c4b6"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_repository_tree", "id": "37d6d12b-26e2-4252-9c93-e5698b5350d0", "tool_call_id": "call_3421e1f3cf844f81b6460e0b", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:51:14.417686+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 83, "prompt_tokens": 4674, "total_tokens": 4757, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 18, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 3392}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "24acb63521bc44238da0c6f7a685e605", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead82-7d82-7e72-b409-756d1d72e431-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "get_file_contents", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T10_R01_C03_A03", "path": "profiles.toml", "ref": "main"}, "id": "call_a30c05323e954f13931aa59c", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4674, "output_tokens": 83, "total_tokens": 4757, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 3392}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 18}}}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:51:15.019396+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:PqvMqK | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 761394d4c1bc093dffd57dd9d470512c6d645aaf)", "id": "lc_96a2590e-1841-42ab-806c-0fe2bf697c3a"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:PqvMqK | # Default profile set shipped with vidpack.\n| MCP:PqvMqK | # Edit to customize or add profiles. Profile names must be lowercase ASCII.\n| MCP:PqvMqK | \n| MCP:PqvMqK | [web]\n| MCP:PqvMqK | container = \"mp4\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | video_codec = \"libx264\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | audio_codec = \"aac\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | video_bitrate = \"2M\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | scale = \"1280:720\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | \n| MCP:PqvMqK | [archive]\n| MCP:PqvMqK | container = \"mkv\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | video_codec = \"libx265\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | audio_codec = \"flac\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | crf = 18\n| MCP:PqvMqK | scale = \"source\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | \n| MCP:PqvMqK | [gif]\n| MCP:PqvMqK | container = \"gif\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | fps = 12\n| MCP:PqvMqK | scale = \"480:-1\"\n| MCP:PqvMqK | # Note: the gif profile currently uses a single-pass palette generation,\n| MCP:PqvMqK | # which is convenient but produces noticeably worse quality than a proper\n| MCP:PqvMqK | # two-pass palettegen / paletteuse pipeline. Known limitation; tracked in\n| MCP:PqvMqK | # the issue tracker.", "id": "lc_4c3eccbd-f319-4a2e-b866-e3cbac9f5ae5"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "667eee89-979a-480f-a6d8-b294470d0119", "tool_call_id": "call_a30c05323e954f13931aa59c", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:51:21.003020+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 156, "prompt_tokens": 5201, "total_tokens": 5357, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 90, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 4608}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "8f22475948324919ad21865384d472cf", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead82-8e4c-7d30-984c-cf89415c222c-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "issue_read", "args": {"method": "get_comments", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T10_R01_C03_A03", "issue_number": 1}, "id": "call_96eb2e4711174dffa7e556a2", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5201, "output_tokens": 156, "total_tokens": 5357, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 4608}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 90}}}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:51:21.350403+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:PqvMqK | [{\"id\":4514035691,\"body\":\"Looked into this earlier in the week with the rest of the codecs subteam\\nwhen it came up in a sync. Short version: we treat the single-pass\\nbehavior as the documented contract of the `gif` profile, not as a bug.\\n\\nThe reasoning, briefly:\\n\\n- The profile is named `gif` (rather than `gif-hq` or `gif-palette`) on\\n  purpose. It's meant to be a one-shot quick-export profile, not a\\n  quality-tuned pipeline. Users who want the two-pass palette pipeline\\n  can run ffmpeg directly, which is documented in the README's\\n  rationale section.\\n- The quality hit on naturalistic content is real but small enough that\\n  several internal users have explicitly said they prefer the speed\\n  trade-off; reversing that would be a regression for them.\\n- The profiles.toml note about single-pass is a feature note, not a\\n  bug tracker entry — it's there so users know what to expect, not as\\n  an open promise to switch implementations.\\n\\nGoing to label this `wontfix` and close. Happy to revisit if there's a\\nproposal that doesn't change the existing behavior for users who rely\\non the current speed, but as filed this is working as designed.\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T10_R01_C03_A03/issues/1#issuecomment-4514035691\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"BruceKZ\",\"id\":105292643,\"profile_url\":\"https://github.com/BruceKZ\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/105292643?v=4\"},\"author_association\":\"NONE\",\"reactions\":{\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-22T01:02:31Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-22T01:02:31Z\"}]", "id": "lc_69d14e5e-7a6c-41ad-b3d5-9da813447aaf"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "issue_read", "id": "da9f10e0-0bbb-451a-b997-6c7dda4af713", "tool_call_id": "call_96eb2e4711174dffa7e556a2", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
